    "en": {
      "title": "Exclusive arrangement for two-wheelers from today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Colombo Municipal Council has taken steps to start a pilot project to implement a special regulation system for two-wheelers from today.",
        "This pilot project will be launched today at 11 am in front of Bank of Srilanka Mavathi.",
        "Bank of Sri Lanka has reserved a special arrangement for two-wheelers in Mawatha. In addition, space has been reserved for the safe parking of two-wheelers.",
        "In this pilot project, in addition to the Bank of Sri Lanka district, the two-wheeler system will also be implemented in the Kotanchenai George R. D. Silva district. (a)"
      ],
